6月，[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西部上空有[[低气压|低气压区]]存在<ref name="partagas">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201215/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1901-1904/1902.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1901-1904/1902.pdf | title = Year 1902 | author1 = Jose Fernandez Partagas | author2 = Henry F. Diaz | date = 1997 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | accessdate = 2016-12-05 | location = Miami, Florida | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月12日中午12点，[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]][[天鹅群岛|天鹅群岛]]以北约32公里海域发展出热带低气压。气旋朝[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]移动，于次日清晨增强成热带风暴。6月13日，气旋以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]75公里强度从[[古巴|古巴]]今[[阿尔特米萨省|阿尔特米萨省]]登陆。当晚抵达[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]后，风暴继续强化并达到持续风速每小时95公里的最高强度，然后在{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}晚上23点以最高强度从[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[泰勒县_(佛罗里达州)|泰勒县]]南部的斯坦哈奇（{{lang|en|Steinhatchee}}）附近登陆。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>

进入陆地上空后，气旋向东北移动并缓慢减弱。6月16日中午左右，风暴在[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]东南部上空转变成温带气旋，然后加速向东北移动，于次日在[[魁北克|魁北克]][[安蒂科斯蒂岛|安蒂科斯蒂岛]]附近逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />佛罗里达州部分地区测得热带风暴强度大风<ref name="partagas" />，“猎鹰号”（{{lang|en|Falcon}}）汽船在[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]最东南端的福尔斯角（{{lang|en|False Cape}}）东南方向约3.2公里近海沉没。6月16日，[[弗雷德里克斯堡_(弗吉尼亚州)|弗雷德里克斯堡]]和[[白金汉县_(弗吉尼亚州)|白金汉县]]的[[新坎顿_(弗吉尼亚州)|新坎顿]]（{{lang|en|New Canton}}）都创下6月的24小时降雨量新纪录，分别达到88和94毫米。当地旱情由此缓慢，对烟草作物尤为有利。<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/vaerly20hur.htm | title = Early Twentieth Century | author1 = David M. Roth | author2 = Hugh Cobb | date = 2001-07-16 | work = Weather Prediction Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-05 | location = Camp Springs, Maryland | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073908/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/vaerly20hur.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>
